OL,3,CCoroner voices fears over 'open and
OL,4,Cfree trade' of drugs at festival after
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA coroner has highlighted concerns
OL,8,Fover an "unchecked, open and free
OL,9,Ftrade" of drugs at Boomtown after a 22-
OL,10,Fyear-old bought MDMA at the festival
OL,11,Fand died.
OL,13,FBenjamin Buckfield took the drug in
OL,14,Fpowder and pill form at the music
OL,15,Fevent outside Winchester last summer.
OL,17,FHe collapsed at the festival and was
OL,18,Ftaken to hospital where he died on
OL,19,FAugust 11 "due to the toxic effects of
OL,20,Fthe drugs", an inquest found.
