OL,3,CCoroner voices fears over 'open and
OL,4,Cfree trade' of drugs at festival after
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FA coroner has called on Boomtown and
OL,8,FHampshire and Isle of Wight
OL,9,FConstabulary to take action to prevent
OL,10,Fmore deaths.
OL,12,FNicholas Walker, area coroner for
OL,13,FHampshire, Portsmouth and Southampton,
OL,14,Fsaid in his report that he has "taken
OL,15,Finto account" the changes made by the
OL,16,Ffestival and the police force for
OL,17,FBoomtown 2025, which is due to kick
OL,18,Foff on Wednesday.
