OL,3,CCoroner voices fears over 'open and
OL,4,Cfree trade' of drugs at festival after
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,FMr Walker said: "I heard evidence that
OL,8,Fillegal drugs were freely available to
OL,9,Fpurchase at the festival.
OL,11,F"One of Ben's friends described how
OL,12,Fdealers would walk through the
OL,13,Fcampsites shouting the names of the
OL,14,Fdrugs they were offering to supply.
OL,16,F"I was told this took place as
OL,17,Fregularly as every 20 minutes and that
OL,18,Fthey saw nothing done to try and
OL,19,Fdisrupt this trade.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
