OL,3,CCoroner voices fears over 'open and
OL,4,Cfree trade' of drugs at festival after
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"I am concerned that an unchecked,
OL,8,Fopen and free trade in unlawful drugs
OL,9,Fwill create a risk of future deaths."
OL,11,FHe continued: "I heard evidence that
OL,12,Fthose found bringing unlawful drugs in
OL,13,Fto Boomtown are not ejected from the
OL,14,Fsite unless they are considered to be
OL,15,Fcarrying quantities that are
OL,16,Fconsistent with being a drug dealer,
OL,17,For they have associated dealer
OL,18,Fparaphernalia.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
