OL,3,CCoroner voices fears over 'open and
OL,4,Cfree trade' of drugs at festival after
OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"Those who are found in possession of
OL,8,Funlawful drugs who are not considered
OL,9,Fto be dealers have their drugs
OL,10,Fconfiscated and are allowed entry on
OL,11,Fto site.
OL,13,F"I am concerned that as a consequence
OL,14,Fthere is no disincentive for festival-
OL,15,Fgoers who attempt to take drugs in to
OL,16,FBoomtown and that the policy gives
OL,17,Frise to a situation where those who
OL,18,Fhave had drugs taken from them will
OL,19,Fwant to replace them.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
