OL,5,Cdeath
OL,7,F"I am concerned that these factors
OL,8,Fgive rise to a demand for, and a
OL,9,Fmarket in, the sale of illegal drugs
OL,10,Fat Boomtown."
OL,12,FThe Boomtown drugs policy states: "We
OL,13,Fdo not condone any usage of drugs at
OL,14,FBoomtown and anyone found in
OL,15,Fpossession of drugs, will have them
OL,16,Fconfiscated and you might be ejected
OL,17,Ffrom the festival site and could face
OL,18,Fprosecution.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
